  "metadata": {
    "role": "article",
    "roleHeading": "Article",
    "title": "Sharing environment variables across Xcode Cloud workflows"
  },
  "primaryContentSections": [
    {
      "content": [
        {
          "anchor": "Overview",
          "level": 2,
          "text": "Overview",
          "type": "heading"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "You can use shared environment variables in your custom build scripts to extend workflows. For example, use a shared environment variable for the location of an IPA file. Then you can edit the values of common environment variables in one location.",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "Before you begin, configure your project to use Xcode Cloud and create two or more workflows to share environment variables with.",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "anchor": "Manage-shared-environment-variables-in-Xcode",
          "level": 3,
          "text": "Manage shared environment variables in Xcode",
          "type": "heading"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "To create shared environment variables in Xcode:",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "items": [
            {
              "content": [
                {
                  "inlineContent": [
                    {
                      "text": "Open your project, click the Report navigator button in the navigator bar, and then click the Cloud button.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "content": [
                {
                  "inlineContent": [
                    {
                      "text": "In the sidebar, Control-click your project name and choose Manage Environment Variables from the pop-up menu.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "content": [
                {
                  "inlineContent": [
                    {
                      "text": "In the lower-left corner of the sheet, click the Add button (+).",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "content": [
                {
                  "inlineContent": [
                    {
                      "text": "In the Shared Environment Variables sheet, enter a name and value for the variable.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "content": [
                {
                  "inlineContent": [
                    {
                      "text": "To securely store the variable and make sure it doesn’t appear in any logs, select the “Keep value redacted” checkbox in the Secret section.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "content": [
                {
                  "inlineContent": [
                    {
                      "text": "To restrict editing of the alias to team roles, select the Only the Account Holder checkbox in the Restrict Editing section.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "content": [
                {
                  "inlineContent": [
                    {
                      "text": "Click Next.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "content": [
                {
                  "inlineContent": [
                    {
                      "text": "In the Select Workflows sheet, select the workflows you want to apply the environment variable to and then click Save.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "content": [
                {
                  "inlineContent": [
                    {
                      "text": "In the Shared Environment Variables sheet, click Done.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                }
              ]
            }
          ],
          "type": "orderedList"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "To edit or delete environment variables in the Shared Environment Variables sheet before you click Done, Control-click the variable, and then choose Edit or Delete.",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "content": [
            {
              "inlineContent": [
                {
                  "text": "You can also choose Integrate > [Your project name] > Manage Shared Environment Variables to create, edit, or delete environment variables.",
                  "type": "text"
                }
              ],
              "type": "paragraph"
            }
          ],
          "name": "Tip",
          "style": "tip",
          "type": "aside"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "To apply environment variables to workflows in Xcode:",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "items": [
            {
              "content": [
                {
                  "inlineContent": [
                    {
                      "text": "In the Report navigator, Control-click your project name and choose Manage Workflows from the pop-up menu.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "content": [
                {
                  "inlineContent": [
                    {
                      "text": "In the detail area of the sheet, Control-click the workflow you want to apply environment variables to, and then choose Edit from the pop-up menu.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "content": [
                {
                  "inlineContent": [
                    {
                      "text": "In the sidebar, click Environment.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "content": [
                {
                  "inlineContent": [
                    {
                      "text": "Under Environment Variables, select the environment variables to apply to the workflow.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "content": [
                {
                  "inlineContent": [
                    {
                      "text": "Click Save.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                }
              ]
            }
          ],
          "type": "orderedList"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "To create another environment variable, click the Add button and choose New Shared Environment Variable from the pop-up menu.",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "anchor": "Manage-shared-environment-variables-in-App-Store-Connect",
          "level": 3,
          "text": "Manage shared environment variables in App Store Connect",
          "type": "heading"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "You can also apply shared environment variables to workflows in App Store Connect with the following steps:",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "items": [
            {
              "content": [
                {
                  "inlineContent": [
                    {
                      "text": "Sign in to your App Store Connect account and go to your app’s page.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "content": [
                {
                  "inlineContent": [
                    {
                      "text": "Click the Xcode Cloud tab.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "content": [
                {
                  "inlineContent": [
                    {
                      "text": "In the sidebar, click Settings.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "content": [
                {
                  "inlineContent": [
                    {
                      "text": "Click the Shared Environment Variables tab.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "content": [
                {
                  "inlineContent": [
                    {
                      "text": "Next to Shared Environment Variables, click the Add button.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "content": [
                {
                  "inlineContent": [
                    {
                      "text": "In the New Shared Environment Variable sheet, enter a name and value for the variable.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "content": [
                {
                  "inlineContent": [
                    {
                      "text": "To securely store the variable and make sure it doesn’t appear in any logs, select the Secret checkbox.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "content": [
                {
                  "inlineContent": [
                    {
                      "text": "To restrict editing of the alias to team roles, select the Only the Account Holder checkbox.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "content": [
                {
                  "inlineContent": [
                    {
                      "text": "Click Next.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "content": [
                {
                  "inlineContent": [
                    {
                      "text": "In the Select Workflows sheet, select the workflows you want to apply the environment variable to.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "content": [
                {
                  "inlineContent": [
                    {
                      "text": "Click Save.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                }
              ]
            }
          ],
          "type": "orderedList"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "To edit or delete custom aliases, click More (…) next to the environment variable and choose Edit or Delete from the pop-up menu.",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        }
      ],
      "kind": "content"
    }
  ],
